// =============================================================================
// {$name$}.jade  —  UI scene for the {$name$} app
// Generated by sdlos create [{$template$}].  Edit freely.
// CSS styles → {$name$}.css  (loaded automatically by jade_host)
// =============================================================================
//
// Layout: single-column flex column — hero title + subtitle placeholder
//
// Node ID reference  (used by tree.findById() in the behavior)
// ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
//   root              — window root column  (flexGrow="1")
//
// EventBus topics fired by this scene (onclick handlers)
// ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
//   None by default.  Add  onclick="{$name$}:<topic>"  to any node and
//   subscribe in {$name$}_behavior.cxx to wire up interactivity.
//
// Layout notes
// ------------
//   col / row  map to CSS flexbox column / row containers.
//   Attribute names are camelCase inline (flexGrow, backgroundColor, …);
//   jade_host applies CSS class rules first, then inline attrs override them.
//   See {$name$}.css for class definitions and the full design-token palette.
// =============================================================================

col(id="root" flexGrow="1")

  div.hero-title {$name$}
  div.hero-sub   Edit {$name$}.jade to get started.
